imdb.title: The Real Housewives of Melbourne
plot: Follows the lives of six wealthy housewives of Melbourne, Australia.
synopsis: The Real Housewives of Melbourne follows the busy, aspirational lifestyles of a group of driven and ambitious women who enjoy the lavish, pampered and cultured lifestyle of Melbourne. Between them, they own private jets, amazing homes and are married to high profile businessmen, including one to a rock star and another to a plastic surgeon.Andrea Moss Moss is a former New York City television journalist who now lives in Toorak. She runs a plastic surgery and cosmetic medicine business, Liberty Belle Skin Centre, with her husband, Dr. Chris Moss. The couple have three children together.Gina Liano - Liano is a barrister. She is a single mother of two and lives in South Yarra.Lydia Schiavello - Schiavello is married to Australian architect and CEO of Metier 3, Andrew Norbury.[5] She is studying interior design and decoration at RMIT University. Schiavello has six children and step-children.Janet Roach - Roach is a property developer. She is a mother of two sons.Jackie Gillies Gillies is a psychic. She is the wife of Silverchair drummer and Bento front man, Ben Gillies.Chyka Keebaugh - Keebaugh is the owner of two event companies, The Big Group and The Design Depot. She has two children.
